---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  pageKey="privacy"
  title="Politika privatnosti – BL Prevoz"
  description="Politika privatnosti BL Prevoz platforme. Informacije o korištenju analitike, kolačića i zaštiti vaših podataka."
  canonicalUrl="https://blprevoz.com/privacy/"
>
  <section class="section section--narrow" id="privacy">
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="section__title" id="privacy-title">
        <span data-lang="bhs">Politika privatnosti</span>
        <span data-lang="en" style="display:none">Privacy Policy</span>
      </h1>

      <div class="privacy-content">
        <!-- Introduction -->
        <div data-lang="bhs">
          <h2>Uvod</h2>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz (<a href="https://blprevoz.com">blprevoz.com</a>) je nezavisna, nekomercijalna platforma za informacije
            o javnom prevozu u Banjoj Luci.
          </p>
          <p>
            Vaša privatnost nam je važna. Ova stranica objašnjava kako koristimo analitiku i kolačiće prilikom
            korištenja ovog sajta.
          </p>

          <h2>Analitika</h2>
          <p>
            Ovaj sajt koristi <strong>Google Analytics 4</strong> kako bismo razumjeli na koji način se sajt koristi
            i kako bismo mogli poboljšati korisničko iskustvo.
          </p>
          <p>
            Analitika se aktivira <strong>isključivo nakon vašeg pristanka</strong> putem banera za kolačiće.
          </p>
          <p>Prikupljaju se isključivo agregirani i anonimizovani podaci, kao što su:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Broj posjeta stranicama</li>
            <li>Trajanje posjete</li>
            <li>Tip uređaja i pretraživača</li>
            <li>Država iz koje se pristupa sajtu (bez precizne lokacije)</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            Ne prikupljamo lične podatke kao što su imena, email adrese, telefonski brojevi niti bilo kakve
            informacije koje mogu direktno identifikovati korisnika.
          </p>
          <p>
            Google Analytics može obrađivati skraćene IP adrese u skladu sa svojim pravilima privatnosti.
          </p>

          <h2>Kolačići</h2>
          <p>Ovaj sajt koristi sljedeće kolačiće i lokalne podatke:</p>
          <p>
            <strong>analytics-consent</strong> (localStorage)<br />
            Čuva vašu odluku o prihvatanju ili odbijanju analitičkih kolačića.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Google Analytics kolačići</strong> (<code>_ga</code>, <code>_gid</code>)<br />
            Postavljaju se samo ako prihvatite analitiku. Koriste se za razlikovanje korisnika i sesija u svrhu
            analize korištenja sajta.
          </p>
          <p>
            Svoju odluku možete promijeniti brisanjem podataka pretraživača (localStorage) ili brisanjem kolačića
            za ovaj sajt.
          </p>

          <h2>Kontakt</h2>
          <p>
            Za sva pitanja u vezi privatnosti možete nas kontaktirati na
            <a href="mailto:blprevoz@proton.me">blprevoz@proton.me</a>.
          </p>

          <h2>Odricanje odgovornosti</h2>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz je nezavisna platforma i nije povezana sa zvaničnim gradskim institucijama niti prevoznicima.
          </p>
          <p>
            Analitički podaci koriste se isključivo za razumijevanje korištenja sajta i unapređenje korisničkog iskustva.
          </p>
          <p>
            Podaci se ne prodaju, ne dijele niti prenose trećim stranama, osim Google Analytics servisu u gore
            opisane svrhe.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- English version -->
        <div data-lang="en" style="display:none">
          <h2>Introduction</h2>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz (<a href="https://blprevoz.com">blprevoz.com</a>) is an independent, non-commercial platform for
            public transport information in Banja Luka.
          </p>
          <p>
            Your privacy is important to us. This page explains how we use analytics and cookies when using this site.
          </p>

          <h2>Analytics</h2>
          <p>
            This site uses <strong>Google Analytics 4</strong> to understand how the site is used and to improve
            the user experience.
          </p>
          <p>
            Analytics is activated <strong>only after your consent</strong> via the cookie banner.
          </p>
          <p>Only aggregated and anonymized data is collected, such as:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Page view counts</li>
            <li>Visit duration</li>
            <li>Device and browser type</li>
            <li>Country of access (no precise location)</li>
          </ul>
          <p>
            We do not collect personal data such as names, email addresses, phone numbers, or any information that
            can directly identify a user.
          </p>
          <p>
            Google Analytics may process truncated IP addresses in accordance with its own privacy policies.
          </p>

          <h2>Cookies</h2>
          <p>This site uses the following cookies and local data:</p>
          <p>
            <strong>analytics-consent</strong> (localStorage)<br />
            Stores your decision to accept or decline analytics cookies.
          </p>
          <p>
            <strong>Google Analytics cookies</strong> (<code>_ga</code>, <code>_gid</code>)<br />
            Set only if you accept analytics. Used to distinguish users and sessions for site usage analysis.
          </p>
          <p>
            You can change your decision by clearing your browser data (localStorage) or deleting cookies for this site.
          </p>

          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>
            For any privacy-related questions, contact us at
            <a href="mailto:blprevoz@proton.me">blprevoz@proton.me</a>.
          </p>

          <h2>Disclaimer</h2>
          <p>
            BL Prevoz is an independent platform and is not affiliated with official city authorities or transport operators.
          </p>
          <p>
            Analytics data is used solely to understand site usage and improve the user experience.
          </p>
          <p>
            Data is not sold, shared, or transferred to third parties, except for the Google Analytics service
            as described above.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
